    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>People who specialize in creating photographs that depict current fashions, usually for advertising or commercial use and often published in fashion magazines or journals.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
